image_analysis.description: A photograph showing an open white door leading into a walk-in closet or storage room. The room containing the door has a dark navy blue or black wall and a light-colored patterned carpet with a geometric diamond/square motif. Inside the closet, there is a built-in storage unit consisting of several rows of white storage boxes on shelves above a set of five wide drawers. To the left of the drawers, a yellow box is visible on the floor. A small sign with 'GG' is visible on the inner wall of the closet.
image_analysis.layout: Interior room view looking through a doorway into a storage area.

notes: The text 'GG' appears on a small white card or label taped to the wall inside the closet. The number 'EFTA00001180' is a Bates stamp used for document identification in legal or investigative proceedings.
